Damage 6 - Delay 38<BR>
Weight: 1.2 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/weapons/piercing.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/enchanter/weapons/piercing.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/weapons/piercing.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/necromancer/weapons/piercing.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/rogue/weapons/piercing.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/wizard/weapons/piercing.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(INT +3) (WIS +3) </font>
<BR>
Found in the burning woods.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 1234pp (59 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 600pp (3 quotes)<BR>

